msgstr "Aplikacije 16.12"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you find settings for home and start page and the behavior of "
"tabbed browsing both for &konqueror;’s file manager and browser mode."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani najdete nastavitve za domačo in začetno stran ter vedenje "
"brskanja z zavihki za upravljalnika datotek &konqueror; in način brskalnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "When Konqueror starts"
msgstr "Ko se Konqueror zažene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option determines which page is displayed when &konqueror; starts, the "
"introduction page, your home page, a blank page or your bookmarks page."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost določa, katera stran je prikazana, ko &konqueror; začetek, uvodna "
"stran, vaša domača stran, prazna stran ali stran z zaznamki."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home page"
msgstr "Domača stran"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the &URL; (&eg; a folder or a web page) where &konqueror; in browser "
"mode will jump to when the <guibutton>Home Page</guibutton> button in the "
"toolbar is pressed. You can set a path that is your <guilabel>Home page</"
"guilabel> by typing into the text field, or using the <guiicon>browse</"
"guiicon> icon to select a local folder. &konqueror; needs to be restarted "
"for changes to take effect."
msgstr ""
"To je &URL; (&eg; mapa ali spletna stran), kjer &konqueror; v načinu "
"brskalnika skoči na, ko pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Domača stran</guibutton> "
"v orodni vrstici. Pot, ki je vaša <guilabel>domača stran</guilabel>, lahko "
"nastavite tako, da vnesete v besedilno polje ali uporabite ikono "
"<guiicon>prebrskaj</guiicon>, da izberete lokalno mapo. &konqueror; je treba "
"znova zagnati, da spremembe začnejo veljati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &konqueror; is used in file manager mode, the <guilabel>Home Page</"
"guilabel> button in the toolbar is replaced by a <guilabel>Home Folder</"
"guilabel> button which makes it jump to your local home folder instead."
msgstr ""
"Ko se &konqueror; uporablja v načinu upravitelja datotek, je gumb "
"<guilabel>Domača stran</guilabel> v orodni vrstici nadomeščen z gumbom "
"<guilabel>Domača mapa</guilabel>, zaradi česar skoči v vašo lokalno domačo "
"mapo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open links in new tab instead of in new window"
msgstr "Odpri povezave v novem zavihku namesto v novem oknu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; defaults to a single window per page, but has the capability to "
"open multiple <firstterm>tabs</firstterm> inside a single window. "
"&konqueror; also, by default, has a &MMB; shortcut to open any link in a new "
"window. If you enable <guilabel>Open links in new tab instead of in new "
"window</guilabel> you can &MMB; click on a link to have it open in a new tab."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror; privzeto ima eno okno na stran, vendar ima možnost odpreti več "
"<firstterm>zavihkov</firstterm> v enem oknu. &konqueror; privzeto ima tudi "
"&MMB; bližnjico za odpiranje katere koli povezave v novem oknu. Če omogočite "
"<guilabel>Odpri povezave v novem zavihku namesto v novem oknu</guilabel>, "
"lahko &MMB; kliknite na povezavo, da se odpre v novem zavihku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open popups in new tab instead of in new window"
msgstr "Odpri pojavna okna v novem zavihku namesto v novem oknu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether or not JavaScript popups if allowed shall open in a new tab or in a "
"new window."
msgstr ""
"Ali se bodo pojavna okna JavaScript, če so dovoljena, odprla v novem zavihku "
"ali v novem oknu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open as tab in existing Konqueror when URL is called externally"
msgstr "Odpri kot zavihek v obstoječem Konquerorju, ko je URL poklican zunaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click a &URL; in another &kde; program or call kfmclient to open a "
"&URL;, the current desktop will be searched for a nonminimized &konqueror; "
"and, if found, the &URL; opened as a new tab within it. Otherwise a new "
"&konqueror; window will be opened with the required &URL;."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete &URL; v drugem &kde; programu ali pokličite kfmclient, da "
"odprete &URL;, bo na trenutnem namizju preiskan neminimiziran &konqueror; "
"in, če je najden, &URL; se odpre kot nov zavihek v njem. V nasprotnem "
"primeru se bo odprl novi &konqueror; v oknu z zahtevanim &URL;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open new tabs in the background"
msgstr "Odpiranje novih zavihkov v ozadju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using tabbed browsing, you can choose if a newly opened tab "
"becomes the active (<quote>front</quote>) tab, or goes to the back. On a "
"slow Internet connection, or while browsing a page that has a list of "
"headlines or other links in a list, you may like to have the new tabs load "
"in the background while you continue reading. In this case, enable this "
"setting. If you prefer to go straight to the new page, leaving the old one "
"in the background to return to later, disable it."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate brskanje z zavihki, lahko izberete, ali na novo odprt zavihek "
"postane aktiven (<quote>sprednji</quote>) zavihek ali gre na zadnjo stran. "
"Pri počasni internetni povezavi ali med brskanjem po strani, ki ima seznam "
"naslovov ali drugih povezav na seznamu, boste morda želeli, da se novi "
"zavihki nalagajo v ozadju, medtem ko nadaljujete z branjem. V tem primeru "
"omogočite to nastavitev. Če želite iti naravnost na novo stran in pustiti "
"staro v ozadju, da se nanjo vrnete pozneje, jo onemogočite."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open new tab after current tab"
msgstr "Odpri nov zavihek za trenutnim zavihkom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will open a new tab opened from a page after the current tab, instead "
"of after the last tab."
msgstr ""
"To bo odprlo nov zavihek, odprt na strani za trenutnim zavihkom, namesto za "
"zadnjim zavihkom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide the tab bar when only one tab is open"
msgstr "Skrij vrstico z zavihki, ko je odprt samo en zavihek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display the tab bar only if there are two or more tabs. Otherwise "
"it will always be displayed."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo vrstico z zavihki le, če sta dva ali več zavihkov. V "
"nasprotnem primeru bo vedno prikazan."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show close button on tabs"
msgstr "Prikaži gumb za zapiranje na zavihkih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display close buttons inside each tab instead of websites’ icons."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo gumbe za zapiranje znotraj vsakega zavihka namesto ikon "
"spletnih mest."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Middleclick on a tab to close it"
msgstr "Srednji klik na zavihek, da ga zaprete"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click on a tab using the middle mouse button or mouse wheel, it "
"will close that tab. &konqueror; needs to be restarted for changes to take "
"effect."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete zavihek s srednjim gumbom miške ali miškinim kolescem, se ta "
"zavihek zapre. &konqueror; je treba znova zagnati, da spremembe začnejo "
"veljati."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Confirm when closing windows with multiple tabs"
msgstr "Potrdi pri zapiranju oken z več zavihki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you close a window in &konqueror; that has multiple tabs open, "
"&konqueror; will ask you if you’re sure that you meant to close it. You can "
"toggle on and off this behavior with this check box."
msgstr ""
"Če zaprete okno v &konqueror; ki ima odprtih več zavihkov, vas bo "
"&konqueror; ali ste prepričani, da ste ga želeli zapreti. To vedenje lahko "
"vklopite in izklopite s tem potrditvenim poljem."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activate previously used tab when closing the current tab"
msgstr "Aktiviraj prej uporabljen zavihek, ko zapreš trenutni zavihek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checking this the previous used or opened tab will be activated when "
"you close the current active tab instead of the one right to the current tab."
msgstr ""
"Če to potrdite, se bo prejšnji uporabljeni ali odprti zavihek aktiviral, ko "
"zaprete trenutni aktivni zavihek namesto tistega desno od trenutnega zavihka."
